Get a column from a table where some rows don't have that column, using the optional flag.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [{A: A0, B: B0}, {B: B1}, {A: A2, B: B2}] | get -o A
в•­в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”¬в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв•®
в”‚ 0 в”‚ A0 в”‚
